## Development

### Running Tests
```bash
cd generateagents-mcp
uv run pytest tests/ -v
```

### Testing MCP compliance
Use the MCP Inspector tool (bundled with mcp package):
```bash
mcp dev server.py
```

This opens an interactive inspector where you can test each tool directly.

